---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Complete Guide to Day Spa Marketing Automation in Canada | Lead Flow North">
  <article class="py-12 md:py-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <!-- Back Link -->
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-8">
        <a href="/industries/salons-spas/day-spas" class="inline-flex items-center text-sky-600 hover:text-sky-700 font-medium">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"></path></svg>
          Back to Day Spas
        </a>
      </div>
      
      <header class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center mb-12">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4 mb-6">
          <span class="bg-teal-100 text-teal-700 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Day Spas</span>
          <span class="text-slate-500 text-sm">10 min read</span>
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6">
          The Complete Guide to Day Spa Marketing Automation
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 mb-8">
          Turn special occasions into regular visits, maximize gift card redemption, and sell packages without the hard sell.
        </p>
      </header>

      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <div class="prose prose-lg prose-slate max-w-none">
          
          <p class="lead text-xl text-slate-700 mb-8">
            Day spas live on occasions—birthdays, anniversaries, holidays. The challenge is converting these one-time visitors into regular guests who see spa visits as self-care, not just special treats.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-12 mb-4">Gift Cards Are Revenue Waiting to Happen</h2>

          <p>
            Unredeemed gift cards sit on your books as liability. "Use your balance" reminders at strategic intervals convert those paper promises into booked treatments—and often, upgraded experiences.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-12 mb-4">Packages Sell Themselves</h2>

          <p>
            Post-visit sequences that share package benefits feel helpful, not pushy. "Loved your massage? Our monthly wellness membership includes one massage plus 20% off additional services."
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-12 mb-4">Seasonal Campaigns That Fill Slow Periods</h2>

          <p>
            January is slow. But automated "New Year, New You" campaigns, "treat yourself" messages, and couples' packages keep rooms filled between the big holidays.
          </p>

          <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-teal-600 to-cyan-600 p-8 rounded-xl text-white my-12">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Ready to Fill Your Treatment Rooms?</h3>
            <p class="text-teal-100 mb-6">
              Get a free consultation and see exactly how we'd turn occasional visitors into loyal members.
            </p>
            <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center bg-white text-teal-600 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-slate-100 transition">
              Book Your Free Demo
            </a>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>
